snippet.title: Q&A session with RollerCoin Team #1 — Meet the hamsters!
snippet.description:
First time ever Question & Answer session with RollerCoin on YouTube 📻

Our team will answer your most common questions found online and share some details related to the upcoming content 🤭

You will have a chance to get your desired answers, find out what's coming next, and even meet our team! 😱

🐹 Follow hamsters on Twitter!
@Play2Earner: https://twitter.com/Play2Earner
@Roller_Zebra: https://twitter.com/Roller_Zebra
@Fairy_Hamster: https://twitter.com/Fairy_Hamster

👇 Find out more about what to expect in the next 4 months 👇 https://rollercoin.com/blog/what-to-expect-on-rollercoin/
